{
  "text": "Moreover, MnP activiy was detected (<140 U/l) in R2 from days 1-20 but not in R1 (Fig. 7b ). The enzyme secreted by P. chrysosporium can minimize wastewater toxicity by degrading phenol [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] and protect microbes in AS, thereby enhancing the community richness in R2.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "21224262",
